flowchart TD
    IN["📥 Content to Save"]

    S1["Step 1: Batch Embed\nConvert ALL text → vectors\nin ONE API call"]

    S2["Step 2: Intra-Batch Dedup\nAre items in this batch\nnearly identical?\nSimilarity ≥ 98% → DROP"]

    S3["Step 3: Find Similar in Storage\nSearch existing records\nfor each item in parallel"]

    S4{"Step 4: Decide Path\nFast or LLM?"}

    FAST["⚡ Fast Path\nAll fields given + no similar found\nSkip LLM — just insert"]

    ANALYZE["🤖 LLM Analyze\nInfer scope, categories,\nimportance, metadata"]

    CONSOLIDATE["🤖 LLM Consolidate\nShould we merge, update,\nor delete existing records?"]

    S5["Step 5: Execute\nDelete + Update + Insert\natomically"]

    OUT["✅ Saved to Storage"]

    IN --> S1 --> S2 --> S3 --> S4
    S4 -->|"Fields given, no similar"| FAST
    S4 -->|"Fields missing"| ANALYZE
    S4 -->|"Similar record found"| CONSOLIDATE
    FAST --> S5
    ANALYZE --> S5
    CONSOLIDATE --> S5
    S5 --> OUT